
This is a super-thin wrapper around google-spreadsheet-ruby.
Its a nascent project to monitor web applications directly to google spreadsheets ( https://github.com/gimite/google-spreadsheet-ruby ).


Warning:
This idea isn't fully baked yet, and it won't work right out of the box.


Un-glamorous Half-Baked Demo: http://bit.ly/guk04P

Install:
git clone git://github.com/knowuh/gdocs_reporting.git
cd gdocs_reporting
rake install

Sample Usage:
command line:
ruby -rubygems -e 'require "gdocs_reporting"; GdocsReporting::WebReporter.run'

irb:
 require 'rubygems'
 require 'gdocs_reporting'
 GdocsReporting::WebReporter.run



